OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife in front of baby
OL,4,Ctold doctor he 'felt he would kill her'
OL,6,FA man who stabbed his wife to death in
OL,7,Ffront of their baby after tracking her
OL,8,Fto a refuge told a doctor he "felt
OL,9,Flike he would kill her" more than a
OL,10,Fyear earlier, a court has heard.
OL,12,FKulsuma Akter, 27, was attacked by her
OL,13,Fhusband Habibur Masum, 26, in a street
OL,14,Fin Bradford while she was pushing
OL,15,Ftheir seven-month-old son in a pram.
