OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife in front of baby
OL,4,Ctold doctor he 'felt he would kill her'
OL,6,FA trial has heard Masum tracked Ms
OL,7,FAkter to a refuge, where she had been
OL,8,Fstaying since January 2024 after he
OL,9,Fallegedly held a knife to her throat
OL,10,Fduring an assault at their home in
OL,11,FOldham in November 2023.
OL,13,FGiving evidence at Bradford Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Tuesday, Masum said the
OL,15,Fcouple met and married in Bangladesh,
OL,16,Fand came to the UK in 2022 after he
OL,17,Fobtained a student visa and enrolled
OL,18,Fon a Masters course to study Marketing.
