OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife in front of baby
OL,4,Ctold doctor he 'felt he would kill her'
OL,6,FThe defendant, who gave evidence
OL,7,Fthrough a Bengali interpreter, said
OL,8,Fthey initially had a long-distance
OL,9,Frelationship as he lived in Aylesbury
OL,10,Fwhile studying and she lived in Oldham
OL,11,Fwith her brother.
OL,13,FHe told the court they had "occasional
OL,14,Fdisagreements or arguments" about when
OL,15,Fthey should live together and she
OL,16,Fwould "block him" when she was angry.
OL,18,FMasum said: "I used to feel if I can't
OL,19,Fbe with her I would die."
