OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife in front of baby
OL,4,Ctold doctor he 'felt he would kill her'
OL,6,FJurors heard in August 2022 Masum was
OL,7,Ffound by police at a tram station,
OL,8,Fwhere he had stayed all night after an
OL,9,Fargument with Ms Akter.
OL,11,FHe was taken to hospital where he told
OL,12,Fa doctor "I feel like I would kill
OL,13,Fher" and said "when he fights with her
OL,14,Fhe feels like he is going to kill her".
OL,16,FMedical notes showed he "disclosed
OL,17,Fthoughts to harm himself and his
OL,18,Fgirlfriend and admitted to carrying a
OL,19,Fknife while having these thoughts".
OL,26,@tD@JOUuD@DO]uD@OOUvD@fO]xD@YOU{D@bO]
