OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife in front of baby
OL,4,Ctold doctor he 'felt he would kill her'
OL,6,FMasum told the trial he had never
OL,7,Fcarried a knife in Ms Akter's presence.
OL,9,FAsked by his barrister Frida Hussain
OL,10,FKC why he had made those comments at
OL,11,Fthe hospital, he replied: "I said, 'I
OL,12,Ffeel I'm having some mental health
OL,13,Fissues and I would like to share
OL,14,Fsomething with the doctor'.
OL,16,F"I just wanted to share all that with
OL,17,Fthe doctor."
OL,19,FThe court heard he was advised to
OL,20,Fregister with a GP and seek support
OL,21,Ffrom his university.
