OL,4,Ctold doctor he 'felt he would kill her'
OL,6,FMasum described feeling "depressed",
OL,7,Fbut said he never sought help from a
OL,8,FGP.
OL,10,FThe court heard he and Ms Akter moved
OL,11,Fin together in September 2022 and
OL,12,Fthere were still arguments.
OL,14,FHe said in July 2023 one of her
OL,15,Fbrothers came to the UK and he
OL,16,Fobjected to him staying with them
OL,17,Fbecause of "privacy and space issues".
