OL,6,FThe court heard on July 5 Ms Akter had
OL,7,Fleft after an argument and was staying
OL,8,Fwith family members, who called the
OL,9,Fpolice saying Masum was threatening to
OL,10,Fkill himself if she did not return.
OL,12,FAsked if he was looking for a knife to
OL,13,Fdo something to himself, Masum said:
OL,14,F"Yes."
OL,16,FHe later denied thoughts of self-harm
OL,17,Fwhen the police attended, it was said.
OL,19,FJurors heard Ms Akter returned and
OL,20,Ftheir child was born in September.
