OL,6,FMasum said after Ms Akter and their
OL,7,Fson moved following the alleged
OL,8,Fassault in November, he was "depressed
OL,9,Fa lot".
OL,11,FThe defendant said: "I used to think a
OL,12,Flot about my son. I was separated from
OL,13,Fmy son and I was missing him a lot.
OL,15,F"I also used to think about my wife. I
OL,16,Fwas thinking I hadn't done anything to
OL,17,Fher, why had she separated me from my
OL,18,Fson."
