OL,6,FMasum said he was unable to focus on
OL,7,Fwork or looking after himself and was
OL,8,Fhaving suicidal thoughts, adding: "I
OL,9,Fthought if I ended my life I wouldn't
OL,10,Fstruggle with this constant pain of
OL,11,Fmissing them."
OL,13,FMasum will continue his evidence on
OL,14,FWednesday.
OL,16,FHe denies murdering Ms Akter on 6
OL,17,FApril last year but has pleaded guilty
OL,18,Fto manslaughter and possession of a
OL,19,Fknife.
